*Čisto* selo je bilo veoma lijepo. (The village was very beautiful.)

*Čistoća* je veoma bitna stvar. (Cleanliness is a very important thing.)

*Čista* voda je neophodna za naše zdravlje. (Clean water is essential for our health.)

*Čiste* ruke su važne za zdravlje. (Clean hands are important for health.)

*Čistimo* stan svakog dana. (We clean the apartment every day.)

*Čistili* smo dvorište. (We cleaned the yard.)

*Čistio* sam svoj automobil. (I cleaned my car.)

*Čistili* smo svoju sobu. (We cleaned our room.)

*Čistili* smo ceste. (We cleaned the streets.)